    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Biome: Mountains, Underdark & Caves</em></p><p>A pale, white-stemmed plant that grows under rocky overhangs or deep within caves. The plant has a remarkably short lifecycle, sprouting, maturing, and wilting within a week following the winter solstice. When broken, it oozes a black ichor that, if injected into the bloodstream, can revive characters from unconsciousness, catatonia, or coma. There is a 1% chance per day over the following week that the recipient will revert to their original state, and the plant will then fail to work on them again.</p>",
